@startuml
title Angular Interview Questions and Answers Repository - Architectural View

package "Angular Interview Q&A Repository" {
    component "README.md" as readme {
        note left
            - High-level project description
            - Navigation through Table of Contents
            - Links to external resources
        end note
    }
    
    component "Q&A Collection" as qa {
        note left
            - Extensive questions and answers
            - Covers Angular topics
            - Organized from basic to advanced
        end note
    }
    
    component "Code Examples" as code {
        note right
            - Illustrates Angular concepts
            - Includes practical examples
        end note
    }
    
    component "LICENSE" as license {
        note right
            - Apache 2.0 license terms
        end note
    }
}

readme --> qa : navigates to
qa --> code : includes
qa --> license : governed by

cloud "External Resources" {
    [YouTube Content]
    [Websites]
    [Social Media]
}

readme --> [YouTube Content] : links to
readme --> [Websites] : links to
readme --> [Social Media] : links to

note bottom of qa
    - Repository follows a knowledge repository pattern
    - Modular content organization
end note

@enduml